		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I know the hardware limitations of the Atari 2600. In this game it comes with a somewhat similar style, but not completely identical <img src="./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" alt=";)" title="Wink" /> Anyway, at the present moment is all (graphics) can still change.<br /><br />The scoring system similar to the old, first Pitfall game. The difference is that the score in the game decreases continuously, the sooner we finish the game, the more points you get.

		
